File: Bafana Bafana beat Mali 2-1 on Sunday. JOHANNESBURG - Bafana Bafana have won this year's edition of the Nelson Mandela Challenge. READ: SABC, Safa announce a four-year broadcast agreement Molefi Ntseki's side led Mali 2-0 at half-time in Port Elizabeth. Dean Furman converted a penalty to put the hosts ahead while Themba Zwane doubled the lead. Mali did pull one back in the second half but were denied an equalizer.